show.description: Controlled by a deadly chip and forced to obey the Viper crime syndicate, Agent Bertha infiltrates the nation's grandest wedding to steal a legendary diamond ring. But a shocking secret affair between the groom’s best friend and the bride throws her mission into chaos. When the betrayed groom catches them—and mistakes Bertha for a guest—he cancels the wedding and declares she will be his new bride.
